&lt;p&gt;Some chairs are pencils.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Conclusions:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;I. Some benches are chairs.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;II. Some tables are pencils.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;III. Some pencils are chairs.&lt;/p&gt;

